[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    545[0m:[38;5;10m[49m The pseudocode below covers the most distinctive recruitment-conversation steps. The chapter 11 patterns from earlier recipes (input safety, identity verification, tool-use, output safety, audit logging, per-cohort monitoring, scope discipline, prompt-injection defense, graceful degradation, citation grounding, crisis-pathway routing) all apply here and are not repeated. The recruitment-specific work concentrates in five places: trial-context loading with strict per-trial isolation, the deterministic eligibility-evaluation engine, the prescreen-capture flow with provenance, the coordinator-handoff orchestration, and the representativeness instrumentation.
